<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Johnnic cautions on Omni shares.</title>
<headline>Johnnic cautions on Omni shares.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-02-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Johnnies Industrial Corp Ltd said on Friday, referring to earlier cautioneries, the implementation of proposals which could have an impact on the share price of Omni Media Corp Ltd were still pending.</p>
<p>It urged Omni shareholders to exercise caution in their dealings until a further announcement was made.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
